data.description: Classic and Charming! This solid brick 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath home is located in the heart of Bethlehem. Offering a prime location for those seeking a vibrant urban lifestyle in a quiet neighborhood. Home needs cosmetic TLC and a fresh coat of paint. Carpets have been pulled out to get you started to make this home your own. All furniture will be removed and all appliances stay. 3rd floor is unfinished and perfect for a home office, den, or playroom.   Bring this home back to life with your style & personal touches!   Immerse yourself in the charm of Historic Bethlehem, with its rich history and vibrant atmosphere just blocks away from your front door. Whether you're exploring the local shops, dining at trendy restaurants, or enjoying the lively nightlife, this home offers the perfect base for your urban adventures. Don't miss out!
